---
import RootLayout from '../layouts/RootLayout.astro';
---

<RootLayout title="Lingo Cards: Privacy-Policy">
  <div class="fixed w-screen h-screen top-0 -z-10 opacity-30 bg-[url('/bg.webp')] bg-cover"></div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl overflow-auto p-4">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold">Lingo-Cards Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to Lingo-Cards! This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data when you use our
      services.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>Lingo-Cards uses the following information from your Google account:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Email: Used for authentication purposes.</li>
        <li>Given Name and Family Name: Concatenated to create a username.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Authenticate your identity using your Google email.</li>
        <li>Create a personalized username for your account.</li>
        <li>Include the username in email templates for personalized messages.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">3. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We take the security of your data seriously. We implement measures to protect your information from unauthorized
        access or disclosure.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">4. Your Choices</h2>
      <p>
        You can choose not to provide certain information, but this may limit your access to certain features of
        Lingo-Cards.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">5. Third-Party Access</h2>
      <p>We do not share your data with third parties without your consent, except as required by law.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">6. Updates to This Policy</h2>
      <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Please review it occasionally for any changes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">7. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at{' '}
        <a class="text-blue-500" href="mailto:lingo-cards-ar@gmail.com"> lingo-cards-ar@gmail.com</a>
        .
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">Last Updated: 1 February 2024</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</RootLayout>

